392
00:19:06,545 --> 00:19:08,681
♪ Gabba‐gabba, gabba‐gabba,
gabba‐gabba, gab ♪

393
00:19:08,681 --> 00:19:10,716
♪ Gabba‐gabba hey,
gabba‐gabba ho ♪

394
00:19:10,716 --> 00:19:12,818
♪ Gabba‐gabba, gabba‐gabba,
gabba‐gabba, gab ♪

395
00:19:12,818 --> 00:19:14,186
Genki.

396
00:19:14,186 --> 00:19:16,288
(singing gibberish)

397
00:19:16,288 --> 00:19:18,290
♪

398
00:19:18,290 --> 00:19:21,394
‐Genki?
‐It's so silly.

399
00:19:21,394 --> 00:19:24,330
‐Holly.
‐What?

400
00:19:24,330 --> 00:19:25,431
Hey!

401
00:19:25,431 --> 00:19:28,334
(laughing)

402
00:19:29,201 --> 00:19:31,837
♪

403
00:19:31,837 --> 00:19:35,207
From now on, the rain
will make me happy.

404
00:19:35,207 --> 00:19:37,309
♪

405
00:19:37,309 --> 00:19:38,978
'chi!

406
00:19:38,978 --> 00:19:41,013
♪

407
00:19:41,013 --> 00:19:42,515
Huh?

408
00:19:42,515 --> 00:19:44,016
Holly!

409
00:19:44,016 --> 00:19:46,318
But it's raining,
for goodness sake!

410
00:19:46,318 --> 00:19:48,888
Don't they know enough
to come in out of the‐‐

411
00:19:48,888 --> 00:19:52,391
(shouting)

412
00:19:52,391 --> 00:19:54,760
(groaning)

413
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:57,363
Okay, ready to sing.

414
00:19:57,363 --> 00:19:59,699
Too late, no more singing.

415
00:19:59,699 --> 00:20:02,802
