416
00:20:02,802 --> 00:20:05,571
(laughing)

417
00:20:05,571 --> 00:20:08,374
♪

418
00:20:08,374 --> 00:20:10,409
Oh, thank you everyone.

419
00:20:10,409 --> 00:20:12,678
Aw shucks, Holly,
you're our pal.

420
00:20:12,678 --> 00:20:14,780
Huh, look.

421
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:19,118
♪

422
00:20:19,118 --> 00:20:20,953
Rain gone.

423
00:20:20,953 --> 00:20:23,022
